OL,3,CThree men convicted for dumping 26,000
OL,4,Ctonnes of illegal waste
OL,6,FThree men have been convicted after
OL,7,F26,000 tonnes of waste was dumped at
OL,8,Fmultiple sites across England,
OL,9,Fincluding three in the West Midlands.
OL,11,FThe major investigation led by the
OL,12,FEnvironment Agency also uncovered
OL,13,Flarge-scale illegal deposits of waste
OL,14,Fin Liverpool, Lancashire, Yorkshire
OL,15,Fand Humberside.
OL,17,FOrganised criminal gang members
OL,18,Fapproached waste facilities and
OL,19,Foffered to dispose of baled waste at
OL,20,Freduced costs, which they later
OL,21,Fabandoned.
