OL,3,CThree men convicted for dumping 26,000
OL,4,Ctonnes of illegal waste
OL,6,FThey are estimated to have avoided
OL,7,Flandfill tax costs in excess of #2.7
OL,8,Fmillion, while the cost of clearing
OL,9,Fthe waste at the landowners' expense
OL,10,Fis estimated at more than #3.2 million.
OL,12,FThe dumping of the waste had a severe
OL,13,Fimpact on the landowners and
OL,14,Fbusinesses nearby, who were forced to
OL,15,Fspend money removing the waste.
OL,17,FFly and rat infestations also caused
OL,18,Fnearby businesses to shut, as well as
OL,19,Fthe closure and demolition of sites.
