OL,6,FThere were also further impacts to the
OL,7,Fenvironment, the victims' health and
OL,8,Fthe neighbouring communities.
OL,10,FMarcus Hughes (53), Richard Hopkinson
OL,11,F(52) and Robert McDonagh (51), have
OL,12,Fall pleaded guilty to various
OL,13,Fenvironmental, company and fraud
OL,14,Foffences.
