OL,3,CThree men convicted for dumping 26,000
OL,4,Ctonnes of illegal waste
OL,6,FBirmingham Crown Court heard the gang
OL,7,Fentering into rental or lease
OL,8,Fagreements with owners of land, farms,
OL,9,Findustrial units and, in one instance,
OL,10,Fan operational airfield, under the
OL,11,Ffalse pretences of storing plastic
OL,12,Fpellets and motor vehicles or for the
OL,13,Ftemporary storage of refuse derived
OL,14,Ffuel for later exportation to
OL,15,Fincinerators abroad.
OL,17,FThe baled waste, normally made up of
OL,18,Fhousehold or business waste, was then
OL,19,Fabandoned at the sites.
