OL,6,FThey also diverted the waste to sites
OL,7,Fwhich were owned but unused, forcing
OL,8,Fentry and depositing bales of waste.
OL,9,FThis method was highly organised and
OL,10,Fmade to seem legitimate by the gang
OL,11,Fdeploying 'security officers' in hi-
OL,12,Fvis clothing at the entrance to the
OL,13,Fsites.
OL,15,FEmma Viner, Environment Agency
OL,16,FEnforcement and Investigations
OL,17,FManager, said:
