OL,3,CThree men convicted for dumping 26,000
OL,4,Ctonnes of illegal waste
OL,6,F"Operation Cesium was a complex
OL,7,Finvestigation into large-scale waste
OL,8,Fdumps across the country by a gang who
OL,9,Fspared little thought for their
OL,10,Fvictims and the environmental,
OL,11,Ffinancial and health impacts they
OL,12,Fcaused.
OL,14,F"We take our responsibility to protect
OL,15,Fpeople and the environment seriously,
OL,16,Fwhether by stopping large-scale
OL,17,Fdumping or making life harder for
OL,18,Fcriminals by disrupting illegal
OL,19,Factivity through tough and decisive
OL,20,Faction."
